FBIS4-30900 "dreeu105__a94013" FBIS-EEU-94-105-A Daily Report 31 May 1994 ANNEX Czech Republic Chile's Pinochet Arrives on Unofficial Visit Chile's Pinochet Arrives on Unofficial Visit Delegation Begins Talks With Arms Firm AU3105101994 Prague CTK in English 1012 GMT 31 May 94 -- FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY AU3105101994 Prague CTK English BFN [Text] Prague May 31 (CTK) -- The arms trading company Omnipol has opened negotiations with the Chilean military delegation headed by the former dictator Augusto Pinochet, currently chief of Chilean ground forces, Antonin Tomecek from the Omnipol Secretariat told CTK today. Pinochet left the Forum hotel, where he is staying, this morning shortly before 8:00 a.m. [0600 GMT]. The negotiations at which leading Omnipol representatives are present are taking place outside Prague, Tomecek said. Chilean Ambassador to Prague Rolando Byrgin Stein said he and Pinochet met when Pinochet arrived in Prague yesterday. Stein said it was unlikely that they would meet again before Pinochet leaves Prague, adding that he had no information about Pinochet's schedule.
